        "detailed_description": "<h1>VR Support</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tak</strong>e  <strong>you</strong>r  <strong>table</strong>top  <strong>gami</strong>ng  <strong>to</strong>  <strong>a</strong>  <strong>who</strong>le  <strong>ne</strong>w  <strong>lev</strong>el  <strong>in</strong>  <strong>virt</strong>ual  <strong>real</strong>ity  <strong>wit</strong>h  <strong>th</strong>e  <strong>HT</strong>C  <strong>Viv</strong>e  <strong>&amp;</strong>  <strong>Ocul</strong>us  <strong>Rif</strong>t!  <strong>An</strong>d  <strong>what</strong>'s  <strong>mor</strong>e,  <strong>bot</strong>h  <strong>VR</strong>  <strong>an</strong>d  <strong>non-</strong>VR  <strong>play</strong>ers  <strong>ali</strong>ke  <strong>ca</strong>n  <strong>pla</strong>y  <strong>toget</strong>her  <strong>in</strong>  <strong>th</strong>e  <strong>sam</strong>e  <strong>gam</strong>e  <strong>roo</strong>m!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crea</strong>te  <strong>you</strong>r  <strong>ow</strong>n  <strong>origi</strong>nal  <strong>game</strong>s,  <strong>impo</strong>rt  <strong>cust</strong>om  <strong>asse</strong>ts,  <strong>autom</strong>ate  <strong>gam</strong>es  <strong>wit</strong>h  <strong>script</strong>ing,  <strong>se</strong>t  <strong>up</strong>  <strong>compl</strong>ete  <strong>RP</strong>G  <strong>dunge</strong>ons,  <strong>manipu</strong>late  <strong>th</strong>e  <strong>physi</strong>cs,  <strong>crea</strong>te  <strong>hing</strong>es  <strong>&amp;</strong>  <strong>join</strong>ts,  <strong>an</strong>d  <strong>of</strong>  <strong>cour</strong>se  <strong>fli</strong>p  <strong>th</strong>e  <strong>tab</strong>le  <strong>whe</strong>n  <strong>yo</strong>u  <strong>ar</strong>e  <strong>losi</strong>ng  <strong>th</strong>e  <strong>gam</strong>e.  <strong>Al</strong>l  <strong>wit</strong>h  <strong>an</strong>  <strong>eas</strong>y  <strong>to</strong>  <strong>us</strong>e  <strong>sy